<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Jun1915"><font color="red">16 June 1915</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> (JJ to Stanislaus Joyce): [in German] We are still here and in good health. I hope you are the same. If we leave I will write you. Don&apos;t worry about us. Up to now we have been well treated. I have written something. The first episode of my new novel <cite>Ulysses</cite> is written. The first part, the Telemachiad, consists of four episodes: The second of fifteen, that is, Ulysses&apos; wanderings: and the third, Ulysses&apos; return home, of three more episodes. </div>
